markdownRemark.excerpt:
一杯/いっぱい：one cup, full
Examples/例
俺の心はずっと君でいっぱいなんだよ：my heart is always full of you (Tsuukin Kareshi CD drama as narrated by Hosoya Yoshimasa)
お腹が一杯です: i am full
